VALUES ('5ba87d58-b8c6-4c8a-94d6-356cfbc966ce', 'Which choice completes the text with the most logical transition?', 'That the method succeeded in the metropolitan laboratories, where funding and instruments were never scarce, is a fact the standard history of quantum biology reports without qualification. ______ the provincial workshops, lacking those advantages yet reporting comparable results, expose a confound—patronage, not technique—that the celebratory account, fixed on outcomes, quietly omits.', 'passage', '[{"id":"A","text":"Despite this established prior premise,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Reciprocal Error] A defensible misreading encodes a different relationship than the passage''s rhetorical direction."},{"id":"B","text":"Drawn from this established premise,","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct: the five-word phrase encodes the causal relationship the two nested sentences require."},{"id":"C","text":"Quite apart from this premise,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Rhetorical Misclassification] A defensible misreading encodes a different relationship than the passage''s rhetorical direction."},{"id":"D","text":"Running counter to this premise,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Reciprocal Error] A defensible misreading encodes a different relationship than the passage''s rhetorical direction."}]'::jsonb, 'B', 'Logical Reconstruction:
