VALUES ('b6f9e70c-17bd-4df1-968b-d558a548c226', 'Based on the texts, how would the author of Text 2 most likely respond to the causal claim in Text 1?', 'Text 1
Text 1 assigns causal primacy to the displacement of a regional measurement system in musicology, treating the indexed factor as the engine of the observed pattern.

Text 2
